#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Only the products with the Is Refrigerant setting are available for "
"selection\n"
"                    from the field service worksheet."
msgstr ""
"В ведомости работ выездного сервиса доступны для выбора только товары с\n"
"                    настройкой «Является хладагентом»."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open her Lots/Serial Numbers from the smart buttons at the top of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Откройте ее «Партии/Серийные номера» через смарт-кнопки в верхней части "
"экрана."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open now the Fourth Company order.<br/>Since those products come with\n"
"                        serials, you need to input them. Click on the "
"Details button for each line\n"
"                        and fill in the serial numbers.<br/>Once done, you "
